FREEDOM FOUNDATION, Petitioner,
v.
SERVICE EMPLOYEES INTERNATIONAL UNION LOCAL 925, Respondent. No. 96262-6 Supreme Court of Washington. DATED at Olympia, Washington, January 10, 2019.

ORDER

¶ 1 This case came before the Court on its January 10, 2019, En Banc Conference to consider the petition for review. A majority of the Court voted in favor of the following result:

¶ 2 Now, therefore, it is hereby

¶ 3 ORDERED:

¶ 4 That the petition for review is granted. Any party may serve and file a supplemental brief within 30 days of the date of this order, see RAP 13.7(d).

For the Court

/s/ Fairhurst, CJ. CHIEF JUSTICE
